{"tid":1584934,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"下年 iPhone 12 會放棄M額，同三星華為旗艦一樣採用「超小前置鏡頭」","createTime":"2019-09-21T11:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T11:49:46.000Z","uid":292737,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d3728f3d1fc3d479ab0f32acaf38f81ebc5d7927","tid":1584934,"uid":292737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QHZLuZu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHZLuZu.jpg&h=1186ff70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣光學設備商大立光電 (Largan Precision) 研發既「超小前置鏡頭」<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將會獨家供貨俾 iPhone 12系列, Samsung S11系列, Huawei P40系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信類似今年 Samsung S10, Note 10 既前置針孔鏡頭，但更加細，更加唔覺眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下年終於唔使再對住M額啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612ce2fbd51dc3f5c4100fd5c43faed15072e839","tid":1584934,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:10:57.000Z","msg":"[行動又無人理？] 全球最大親子抗爭活動上線啦！ <strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">#birdfoldingchallenge</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1584614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1584614</a><br />\n摺一隻紙鳥，影相，放上Facebook / Twitter / Instagram，並加上hashtag #birdfoldingchallenge #929globalmarch #929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism，copy呢段文字再tag 5個朋友，就完成！</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYhkXcO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYhkXcO.jpg&h=9b11593e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5101d0c74afcb2a53ef0cf3150d1b6bd567b428","tid":158493